anager not available\"}\n  Line 591: | `session_manager_test.go` | GetSandboxBySession, create via Workload Manager, error cases |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 11: Define the HTTP reverse proxy core for the AgentCube Router component. This provides session-aware routing that resolves session IDs from request headers, creates sandboxes via Workload Manager, forwards HTTP requests to sandbox pod endpoints using `httputil.ReverseProxy`, generates RS256-signed JWT tokens, updates session activity timestamps, and limits concurrent requests via semaphore middleware.\n  Line 129: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/session_manager.go`\n  Line 135: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/session_manager.go`\n  Line 144: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/session_manager.go`\n  Line 152: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/session_manager.go`\n  Line 177: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/session_manager.go`\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 138 matches (38 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":138,"truncated":true},"title":"AR-010|Router.*session|session.*manager","time":{"start":1775851756895,"end":1775851756920}}}}
